========
Vindicta's raid tool OSE (Open Source Edition)
========

Demo : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AeX7VMAuy38 (Smash count + rotation in phase 2, left, middle, right position of marked)

This is a simple addon for World Of Warcraft working like "Client / server" to help your guild on diffrent encounter (Blackhand, Maidens, Gruul), the code is dirty cause i made it quickly


You should make some modification to make it working for you (config.lua), also there is the "client" wich is a weak aura to import :
